(1, 'Standard Loading Ramp Kit - AUN 210 - UNASSEMBLED\r\n', '', 1, 'Standard automated motorcycle loading ramp. Ideal ...', 'EZ Cycle Ramp\'s innovative automated motorcycle loading ramp is designed to make loading and unloading your motorcycle effortless. Our ramp slides straight out like a cargo slide but also tilts to make loading and unloading motorcycles and cargo more manageable. The ramp is cordless tool driven, with no need to draw wires or drill holes in the cargo bed, making installation a breeze.', 'Our ramp is lightweight and durable, constructed from Aerospace-Grade T6 6061 Aluminum Alloy. It can be cut to size or extended to carry choppers, and its metal parts are zinc-plated and powder coated for added protection.', 'Equipped with extenders, the ramp can lift bikes to 1.5 meters, and it is compatible with pick-up trucks, vans, lifted/adventure trucks, and other cargo vehicles. The ramp\'s lift system uses a fin-cooled, oil-submerged, self-locking worm drive, and the recommended torque for the cordless tool to power the worm drive is 60Nm (18 or 24V professional tools will do).', 'With quick and simple adjustments, our ramp is fully adjustable to accommodate almost any size wheel and tire combo. Its tie-down \"T\"-bar adds no increased load on forks, and it can load up to 1200 lbs up to 36\" height (AC001 kit, sold separately, allows up to 60\" load height).', 'No more nightmares of riding your expensive bike in and out of your vehicle. The ramp is fat tire-friendly, accommodating up to a 300mm rear tire, and a tire guide (optional accessory) is available to guide the rear tire onto the ramp safely. The ramp raises the bike only 2 1/2\" off the surface of the cargo bed, allowing it to be used with vans with low overheads. Compared to other models on the market, its improved COG (center of gravity) makes it a safe and reliable choice for motorcycle loading and unloading. Try our automated motorcycle loading ramp today and experience the ultimate convenience of motorcycle loading and unloading!', 'images/AUN200.png', 3100.00, 'Durable anodized black rails are lightweight, strong, and corrosion-resistant for long-lasting use.', '\"Power Tilt\" hydraulic cylinders slide motorcycles out past the bed and quickly down to the ground.', 'Computer-designed wheel chock adapts to most tire widths and diameters, ensuring a secure and stable loading experience.', 'Versatile framework easily installs in trucks, vans, and other cargo vehicles, providing effortless motorcycle loading and unloading.', 'Various supplementary accessories are available to enhance and expand the features of the ramps.', '98 in', '187 lb', '35 in *', '79 in', '1212 lb', '2500 mm', '85 kg', '900 mm *', '2000 mm', '550 kg', '* With the standard AC001 extender, the max loading height can be \r\n		increased to 1300 mm (51 in). With a longer AC001 extension, it can be increased to 1500 mm (59 in).', 'AUN200 Assembly Manual Rev4', 50, 1),
(3, 'Ramp Extension - AC001', 'AC001', 2, 'The perfect solution for those seeking to add length to their tilt frame. With its quick-release brackets, this extender easily clips onto your tilt frame, allowing for extra length and an increased load height.', 'The standard AUN 200 ramps can lift motorcycles to 90 cm or approximately 2 feet 11 inches. But with the addition of the AC001 extender, motorcycles can now be raised to 1.3 meters or about 4 feet, or even higher with a longer extender.', 'This versatile extender is compatible with other accessories, such as the AC008 (cargo loader kit) or the AC006 (snowmobile adapter), making it a great addition to any adventure truck or higher-than-normal truck.', 'If you have a bike with a long exhaust pipe, the AC001 is a must-have accessory. It prevents your bike from scraping the ground during loading and unloading. It is also necessary for bikes with full front fenders as it keeps the loading angle lower to clear the front wheel chock.', NULL, NULL, 'images/AC001.png', 385.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AC _001_installation_2020_01', 100, 1),
(4, 'Van Extension Kit - AC003', '', 2, 'The ultimate accessory for loading motorcycles with large overhangs into vans. This kit attaches to the main frame of your ramp and allows you to slide your bike further into the van, enabling you to easily close the back doors.', 'Compatible with the AUN-200 ramp, the Van Ramp Extender Kit is a versatile addition to your loading equipment. It is also compatible with all other accessories, providing even more functionality.', 'Available in different lengths, the standard length of the Van Ramp Extender Kit is 250mm (approximately 9.8 inches). Don\'t let large overhangs and awkward loading angles hold you back any longer – add the Van Ramp Extender Kit to your arsenal today and make loading your motorcycle into your van a breeze.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'images/AC003.png', 210.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 30, 1),
(6, 'Cargo Loader - AC008 (Model 1)', 'AC008 (Model 1)', 2, 'The ultimate accessory for transporting a wide range of cargo. Whether you need to transport buggies, jet skis, lawn mowers, pallets, 44-gallon drums, or general cargo, the AC008 covers you.', 'The AC008 comes as a chassis where clients can choose what type of floor they want. For example, a floor is not needed for transporting a jet ski. The AC008 fits either the AUN100 or AUN200 ramp and can also be used to transport two motorcycles if their combined weight does not exceed 550kg or approximately 1200 pounds.', 'The AC008 is delivered as a kit and is compatible with AC001, AC003, and AC004. The AC008 sits flat on the ground during loading, making it easy to load and unload cargo. It can even be converted into a container or a tiny camping unit. In addition, the AC008 kit can also function as a Slide-out. The access ramp flips down for easy loading and folds up during transport, allowing you to display your vehicle tag.', 'The AC008 Cargo Loader Adapter Kit comes with 8 attachment hooks to attach straps and skids included for loading in snow or mud. It is delivered in a compact box for easy transportation.', 'This is the original ground cargo loader for Pickups – beware of copies! The AC008 comes in two lengths to fit either the AUN100 ramp or the AUN200, and the width can be customizable for an added fee, ranging from 300 mm (11 ¹³/₁₆ inches) to 1200 mm (3 feet 11¹/₄ inches). The standard width is 1000 mm (3 feet 3 ³/₈ inches).', 'Don\'t settle for anything less than the best – add the AC008 Cargo Loader Adapter Kit to your accessories collection today and enjoy the convenience of easily transporting a wide range of cargo.', 'images/AC008.png', 780.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AC-008 Model 1 installation manual', 50, 1),
(7, 'Boltless Ramp Tie Down - AC012', 'AC012', 2, 'The ultimate accessory for attaching your ramp to vehicles without drilling holes in the cargo bed. With this innovative attach kit, you can easily attach and remove your ramp in a matter of minutes, saving you time and hassle.', 'From a practical point of view, users can easily detach the ramp from one vehicle and then attach it to another, making life easier for many motorcycle owners. Whether you have multiple cargo vehicles or frequently borrow a friend\'s truck, the AC012 Boltless Attach Kit lets you quickly transfer your ramp between vehicles without drilling or permanent modifications.', 'In addition to its practical benefits, the AC012 Boltless Attach Kit is also designed with safety in mind. By eliminating the need for drilling holes in your cargo bed, you can preserve the integrity of your vehicle\'s structure and ensure that it remains solid and secure. This innovative attach kit is also incredibly durable, ensuring that it will provide reliable performance for years to come.', 'Easy to use and versatile, the AC012 Boltless Attach Kit is a must-have accessory for any motorcycle owner. Whether transporting your bike to a rally or moving it from one location to another, this attached kit makes it easy to get the job done quickly and efficiently.', 'Don\'t let the hassle of drilling holes or permanently modifying your vehicle\'s cargo bed hold you back any longer. Add the AC012 Boltless Attach Kit to your accessories collection today and enjoy the convenience of attaching and removing your ramp in minutes.', NULL, 'images/AC012.png', 450.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'AC _012_installation_2021_01', 20, 1),
